{"ops":[{"insert":"基本用途"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"这是一个时区选择器组件（TimezoneSelect），用于在前端界面中让用户从预定义的时区列表中选择一个时区。\n\n主要功能"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"1. 时区选择：展示一个下拉选择框，包含预定义的时区列表供用户选择\n2. 时区信息显示：在选择框触发区域显示当前选中的时区名称和时区偏移信息\n3. UTC 偏移显示：同时显示该时区相对于 UTC 的偏移量（如 UTC+8）\n4. 双向数据绑定：支持 v-model 双向绑定，可以获取和设置当前选中的时区\n5. 搜索功能：支持在时区列表中进行搜索过滤\n6. 事件通知：当时区改变时，会触发 change 事件通知父组件\n\n使用方法"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"plain"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"<template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  <TimezoneSelect v-model=\"selectedTimezone\" @change=\"handleTimezoneChange\" />"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"<script>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"import TimezoneSelect from './TimezoneSelect.vue'"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"export default {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  components: {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    TimezoneSelect"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  },"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  data() {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    return {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      selectedTimezone: '' // 初始时区值"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    }"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  },"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  methods: {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    handleTimezoneChange(timezone) {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      console.log('选择的时区:', timezone)"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      // 处理时区变更逻辑"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    }"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  }"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"}"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</script>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"\nProps 属性"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"- `value` (String): 当前选中的时区值，支持 v-model 双向绑定\n- `onChange` (Function, 可选): 时区改变时的回调函数，接收选中的时区值作为参数\n\n工作原理"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"1. 组件内部维护一个时区列表（从 ./timezone 导入）\n2. 当 value 属性变化时，通过 Watch 监听并更新本地状态和显示信息\n3. 用户选择时区后，通过 handleSelected 方法更新显示信息并通过 emit 触发 change 事件\n4. 渲染时使用蓝鲸 UI 的 bk-select 组件展示时区选项，每个选项显示时区名称、偏移信息和 UTC 偏移标签\n"}],"extra":{"updator":"Austin","update_at":"2026-01-21 17:55:25"}}